column5: Thank you so much for your kind review. It is very helpful to me writing down and drawing my psychological and emotional journey. It is a kind of open source personal diary.
Thank you so much! But beware, it won't be a happy / relaxing comic to read, tho.
Let me know what you think after reading it :)
Hi! Thanks for your comment and advice! I will keep it into consideration while making volume 2. I'm from northern italy.
Yeah. It's hard to find a balance between the two things :(
I feel that too! So true...
